<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Welcome to Our Store!</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: 'Arial', sans-serif;
            line-height: 1.6;
            color: #333;
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 20px;
        }
        .header {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #4facfe 0%, #00f2fe 100%);
            color: white;
            padding: 40px;
            text-align: center;
            border-radius: 10px 10px 0 0;
        }
        .content {
            background: #f9f9f9;
            padding: 30px;
            border-radius: 0 0 10px 10px;
        }
        .features {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
            gap: 15px;
            margin: 25px 0;
        }
        .feature {
            background: white;
            padding: 15px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            text-align: center;
            border-left: 4px solid #4facfe;
        }
        .button {
            display: inline-block;
            background: #4facfe;
            color: white;
            padding: 12px 30px;
            text-decoration: none;
            border-radius: 5px;
            margin: 20px 0;
        }
        .footer {
            text-align: center;
            margin-top: 30px;
            color: #666;
            font-size: 12px;
        }
        .discount {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #ff9a9e 0%, #fecfef 100%);
            color: white;
            padding: 20px;
            text-align: center;
            border-radius: 8px;
            margin: 20px 0;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="header">
        <h1>Welcome Aboard!</h1>
        <p>Thank you for joining our e-commerce family</p>
    </div>
    
    <div class="content">
        <h2>Hello <%= name %>,</h2>
        
        <p>Welcome to our e-commerce platform! We're thrilled to have you as part of our community.</p>
        
        <div class="discount">
            <h3>üéâ Special Welcome Offer!</h3>
            <p style="font-size: 24px; margin: 10px 0;"><strong>10% OFF</strong></p>
            <p>Your first purchase with code: <strong>WELCOME10</strong></p>
        </div>
        
        <h3>Here's what you can do:</h3>
        <div class="features">
            <div class="feature">
                <strong>üõçÔ∏è Shop</strong>
                <p>Browse thousands of products</p>
            </div>
            <div class="feature">
                <strong>üöö Fast Delivery</strong>
                <p>Quick shipping options</p>
            </div>
            <div class="feature">
                <strong>‚≠ê Reviews</strong>
                <p>Share your experiences</p>
            </div>
            <div class="feature">
                <strong>üíù Wishlist</strong>
                <p>Save your favorite items</p>
            </div>
        </div>
        
        <div style="text-align: center;">
            <a href="<%= storeUrl %>" class="button">Start Shopping Now</a>
        </div>
        
        <p>If you have any questions, feel free to reach out to our support team.</p>
        
        <p>Happy shopping!<br>
        The E-commerce Team</p>
    </div>
    
    <div class="footer">
        <p>&copy; <%= new Date().getFullYear() %> Your E-commerce Store. All rights reserved.</p>
        <p>This is an automated message, please do not reply to this email.</p>
    </div>
</body>
</html>